    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3839472674" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16838387830512882581">Elizabeth Bowen was a mid 20th century Irish writer. While she is known for her novels, she was an extremely under-rated yet gifted story writer. Her stories don&apos;t tend to have a lot of movement or variety, but Bowen makes up for it by being extremely talented with structure. She often knows how to set a scene or place a telling detail at the exact right place so as to gain a reader&apos;s interest. Her dialogue is often also well done. <br/><br/>I don&apos;t know if I would recommend Bowen&apos;s writing for anyone, bu</span>
  <span id="freeText16838387830512882581" style="display:none">Elizabeth Bowen was a mid 20th century Irish writer. While she is known for her novels, she was an extremely under-rated yet gifted story writer. Her stories don't tend to have a lot of movement or variety, but Bowen makes up for it by being extremely talented with structure. She often knows how to set a scene or place a telling detail at the exact right place so as to gain a reader's interest. Her dialogue is often also well done. <br /><br />I don't know if I would recommend Bowen's writing for anyone, but she is a good writer to learn from if you are interested in improving your craft.</span>
