<span id="freeTextContainer6661947749798405077">Since this was a library book, I returned it before really digesting it. I read about three of the stories. I find Bowen a a great writer and I will probably buy this book so I can properly enjoy it. Her style is detailed narratives and long paragraphs. it is the kind of writing that you like to savor rather than rush through to find out what happens...</span>

